This Karamba theme displays the following information:

Time
Date
Uptime
Current Weather (from weather.yahoo.com)
4 day forecast (from weather.yahoo.com)
E-mail(POP3) Checking
Percent free CPU
Free RAM
Free Swap
Free space on Hard Drives (/ and /mnt/windows by default)
Traffic in/out on eth0
XMMS Progress
XMMS Title (Scrolling!)
and has XMMS Controls

To have your city's weather displayed, edit scripts/weather.pl.
Make sure to edit scripts/xmms_title.pl to have the XMMS title shown.
Make sure to put in your username/password/server in scripts/mails.pl to check your e-mail.

Make sure you INSTALL the included font.
